trans-unit.source: The base class for discoverable references using XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: Basisklasse for synlig referanser som bruker XML Web services oppdaging.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference>, and <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> all inherit from DiscoveryReference, and represent the three types of documents discoverable through XML Web services discovery: Service Descriptions, XML Schema Definition (XSD) schemas, and discovery documents, respectively.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference>, og <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>alle arve fra DiscoveryReference, og representerer tre typer dokumenter som er tilgjengelig via XML Web services discovery: beskrivelser av tjenesten, XML-skjema definisjon (XSD) skjemaer og discovery dokumenter, henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference></xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the instance of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol"></xref> used in a discovery process.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir forekomsten av <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol"> </xref> brukt i et søkedataelement.

trans-unit.source: An instance of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol"></xref> used in a discovery process
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol"> </xref> brukes i en prosess for oppdaging

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the default file to use when saving the referenced discovery document, XSD schema, or Service Description.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på standardfilen som skal brukes når du lagrer den refererte discovery-dokumentet XSD-skjema eller tjenestebeskrivelsen.

trans-unit.source: Name of the default file to use when saving the referenced document.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på standardfilen som skal brukes når du lagrer referert til dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: Returns a file name based on the passed URL.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et filnavn basert på den angitte URL-adressen.

trans-unit.source: The URL on which the name of the file is based.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen som navnet på filen er basert på.

trans-unit.source: Name of the file based on the passed URL.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på filen basert på den angitte URL-adressen.

trans-unit.source: Reads the passed <xref:System.IO.Stream> and returns an instance of the class representing the type of referenced document.
trans-unit.target: Viser den innsendte <xref:System.IO.Stream>og returnerer en forekomst av klassen som representerer det henvises til dokumenttype.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: The return value is always an <xref:System.Object>.
trans-unit.target: Den returnerte verdien er alltid <xref:System.Object>.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: However, the underlying type varies, depending on the type of document referenced.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid varierer underliggende typen avhengig av dokumentet refererer til.

trans-unit.source: For instance, a <xref:System.IO.Stream> passed into <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference.ReadDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName> returns an instance of <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en <xref:System.IO.Stream>ble sendt til <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference.ReadDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName>returnerer en forekomst av <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.SchemaReference.ReadDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IO.Stream> containing the reference document.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IO.Stream>som inneholder referansedokumentet.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> with an underlying type matching the type of referenced document.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>med en underliggende type samsvarende referert til dokumenttype.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Downloads the referenced document at <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.Url*> to resolve whether the referenced document is valid.
trans-unit.target: Laster ned refererte dokumentet på <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.Url*>å løse om det refererte dokumentet er gyldig.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.Url*>

trans-unit.source: Downloads the referenced document and then invokes the overloaded Resolve member that takes a MIME type and a <xref:System.IO.Stream>.
trans-unit.target: Laster ned refererte dokumentet og aktiverer overbelastet Løs medlemmet som tar en MIME-type og <xref:System.IO.Stream>.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: If the MIME type and the contents of `stream` match those expected by the reference type, then the contents of `stream` are added to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> properties of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis MIME-typen og innholdet i `stream` samsvarer med plattformene som var forventet av referansetypen og innholdet i `stream` legges til <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A>Egenskaper for <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol*> property is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol*>egenskapen <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol*>

trans-unit.source: Resolves whether the referenced document is valid.
trans-unit.target: Løser om refererte dokumentet er ugyldig.

trans-unit.source: If the MIME type and the contents of `stream` match those expected by the reference type, then the contents of `stream` are added to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> properties of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis MIME-typen og innholdet i `stream` samsvarer med plattformene som var forventet av referansetypen og innholdet i `stream` legges til <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A>Egenskaper for <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Documents%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>

trans-unit.source: The MIME type of `stream`.
trans-unit.target: MIME-typen for `stream`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IO.Stream> containing the referenced document.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IO.Stream>som inneholder det refereres til dokumentet.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL of the referenced document.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URL-adresse for det refererte dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the referenced document.
trans-unit.target: URL-adresse for det refererte dokumentet.

trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, skriver dokumentet <xref:System.IO.Stream>.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.target: Dokumentet for å skrive til en <xref:System.IO.Stream>.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IO.Stream>som den `document` skrives.</xref:System.IO.Stream>
